
required libraries :
 - libextlib-ocaml-dev 

additional libraries (enable compilation with --with-<library>) :
 - libpostgresql-ocaml-dev
 - libsqlite3-ocaml-dev
 - libzip-ocaml-dev 
 - libjson-static-camlp4-dev
 - libocamlgraph-ocaml-dev
 - libounit-ocaml-dev

To compile from git :
aclocal -I m4
autoconf
./configure
make

--with-rpm
--with-xml
--with-ocamlgraph
--with-sqlite
--with-postgresql
--with-zip
--with-oUnit

libcudf is included in the source tree of dose3. 
To use libcudf as an ocamlfind external library you can specify
--with-libcudf as configure option.

Ex :
./configure --with-xml --with-ocamlgraph --with-zip --with-oUnit

In order to compile the applications do a "make applications".
